fields.name: ActiveDirectoryGroupId
fields.description: The AAD group ID which this lab roster is populated from. Having this set enables AAD sync mode.

fields.name: LmsInstance
fields.description: The base URI identifying the lms instance.

fields.name: LtiClientId
fields.description: The unique id of the azure lab services tool in the lms.

fields.name: LtiContextId
fields.description: The unique context identifier for the lab in the lms.

fields.name: LtiRosterEndpoint
fields.description: The uri of the names and roles service endpoint on the lms for the class attached to this lab.
